Parses elements (sentences, lists, tables) in governing documents to classify important types and categories For more information, see [Element classification](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/discovery?topic=discovery-element-classification).

[Smart Document Understanding](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/discovery?topic=discovery-sdu) is unavailable if this enrichment is used.



 Enrichment pricing 

